header.gameNote: NEW YORK LIFE ACC MEN'S TOURNAMENT - SEMIFINAL

videos.description: Duke's Trevon Duval gets tangled up with another player and rolls his ankle before leaving the game.
videos.headline: Duval rolls ankle and leaves game

videos.description: Kenny Williams makes a nice extra pass to Luke Maye who hits the jumper.
videos.headline: Nice ball movement lead to Maye jumper

videos.description: Marvin Bagley III throws down the dunk for his first field goal of the game.
videos.headline: Bagley with a two-handed flush

videos.description: Luke Maye sends Marvin Bagley III to the floor with a big block.
videos.headline: Maye gets up and stuffs Bagley

videos.description: Theo Pinson finds Sterling Manley for the bucket while sitting on his behind.
videos.headline: Pinson makes crafty assist from his backside

videos.description: Grayson Allen gets in the way of Garrison Brooks, causing him to fall and then gets called for a flagrant foul.
videos.headline: Allen gets flagrant 1 for intentional hip check

videos.description: Joel Berry II sprints down the court and hits Cameron Johnson for the layup right at the end of the half.
videos.headline: Berry drives the floor and finds Johnson for bucket

videos.description: Seth Greenberg says the play where Grayson Allen was charged a flagrant 1 foul happens "fifty times a game" where Jay Williams adds that Grayson Allen's past played a role in the severity of the call.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Analysis (Greenberg, Williams disagree with flagrant call on Allen) 2018/03/09

videos.headline: Greenberg, Williams disagree with flagrant call on Allen

videos.description: UNC's Kenny Williams comes flying in for the nice rebound and putback in the air.
videos.headline: Williams makes athletic putback

videos.description: UNC's Theo Pinson uses another nice pass to find a cutting Sterling Manley for the dunk.
videos.headline: Pinson finds Manley with a delicious dish

videos.description: UNC's Joel Berry II makes a nice bounce pass to Garrison Brooks for a dunk that gets the bench going.
videos.headline: Berry to Brooks in transition for the rim rocker

videos.description: Marvin Bagley III gets up for a grown man's block on Luke Maye.
videos.headline: Bagley gets Maye back with block

videos.description: Trevon Duval makes a great anticipatory pass to find Grayson Allen for the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Duval finds Allen in the corner for three

videos.description: Grayson Allen forces up a three in the closing seconds of the game, as UNC beats Duke 74-69.
videos.headline: Allen misses potential game-tying three

videos.description: Theo Pinson says he just wanted to make plays as a passer tonight and was happy that his team got the best of their bitter rival.
videos.headline: UNC's Pinson recaps frantic finish
